Housing Price Prediction

This project focuses on predicting housing prices using machine learning techniques. 
The model analyzes various property features such as location, area, number of rooms, and other structural and market-related factors.
The goal is to assist real estate professionals, buyers, and sellers in making data-driven pricing decisions.


